text: I love Telephone Jamaica, before I discovered this site getting credit on our phone's was a nightmare. Thank you so much for making it so easy for us. Anytime I have questions or needed assistance Telephone Jamaica has ALWAYS assisted quickly and very friendly. I always recommend this site to all my friends and sometimes people I don't know ;) ty
